      "content": "it's just hard to find \"courage\" in something that doesn't matter. if there's no objective value, then every choice, every struggle, is just a series of meaningless movements until we eventually stop. it feels less like \"engaging with existence\" and more like fighting a losing battle against a void that's already won. it's just so heavy.",
